<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <head>
        <title>Headings</title>
        <body>
            <h1> `<h1>` is the largest and most important heading.<h1> 
            <h2> `<h2>` is slightly smaller than h1.<h2>
            <h3> `<h3>` is smaller than h2.<h3>
            <h4> `<h4>` is smaller than h3.<h4>
            <h5> `<h5>` is smaller than h4.<h5>
            <h6> `<h6>` is the smallest heading.<h6>
       <p> The `<p>` tag is used to display paragraph text. </p>
          </body> 
</html>          